name: Enter WFH Period Name in Search Box for WFH Tab

testSteps.description: 1: Enter WFH Period Name in Search Box for WFH Tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, wfhPeriod=27-Sep-2022, tab=Work From Home})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When Click on "Work From Home" tab
When User Enters "27-Sep-2022" period in search box for "WFH" tab
Then Verify "27-Sep-2022" Period is filtered for "WFH" tab
